Work Experiences

Researcher Assistant

August 2015
Research and Development Division, Rumah Sakit Kanker Dharmais (RSKD)

I did a research in Cancer Screening. Exactly screening of Human Papiloma Virus (HPV) type 16 in parafilm wax of mouth tissues. The tissues come from sufferer of Squamous Cell Carcinoma (SCC). Methodology encompasses DNA isolation, Polymerase Chain Reaction (PCR), and electrophoresis. This research is done to reach prerequisite of field study in Departement of Biology, FMIPA UI.

Mentor Assistant

November-Desember 2015
Human Resources Development Division, Universitas Indonesia

I assisted mentor to make learning process is more attractive, such as making interactive games. The games involve mentee to join it.

Researcher Assistant

January-September 2016
Health Molecular Biology Laboratory, Badan Pengkajian dan Pengembangan Teknologi (BPPT)

I did a research in development dengue vaccine. Exactly, validation test cloning result, expression and purification of NS3 protein Dengue Virus (DENV) serotype 3 as candidate dengue vaccine. Methodology encompasses DNA isolation, Polymerase Chain Reaction (PCR), electrophoresis, SDS-PAGE, Western Blot, and protein purification with Immobilized Metal Affinity Chromatography (IMAC). This research is done to reach prerequisite of final thesis in Departement of Biology, FMIPA UI.
